dcterms:description: The FB60K-NYT10 dataset includes the FB-60K knowledge graph and the NYT10 corpus. It is used for zero-shot link prediction tasks, where triples (head entity, relation, tail entity) are excluded if either the head entity or the tail entity is not found within the provided knowledge graph.
